        </div>
    	<div class="bigger-box-left">
        <h3>Being part of Lupin means</h3> 
        <ul>
        	<li>being a leader in your field. It means knowing that you are helping millions around the world enjoy better health.</li>
        	<li>taking pride in your work while maintaining the highest ethical standards and best practices that drive our business</li>
        	<li>championing collaboration and teamwork in a diverse team</li>
        	<li>being passionate about new challenges and thinking outside the box</li>
